  <refentry xml:id="function.prev" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>prev</refname>
    <refpurpose>将数组的内部指针倒回一位</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
 <refsect1 role="description">
  &reftitle.description;
  <methodsynopsis>
   <type>mixed</type><methodname>prev</methodname>
   <methodparam><type>array</type><parameter role="reference">array</parameter></methodparam>
  </methodsynopsis>
  <para>
   将数组的内部指针倒回一位。
  </para>
  <para>
     <function>prev</function> 和
     <function>next</function> 的行为类似，只除了它将内部指针倒回一位而不是前移一位。
    </para>
   </refsect1>
    <refsect1 role="parameters">
  &reftitle.parameters;
  <para>
   <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
     <term><parameter>array</parameter></term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       The input array.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="returnvalues">
  &reftitle.returnvalues;
  <para>
   返回数组内部指针指向的前一个单元的值，或当没有更多单元时返回 &false;。
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="examples">
  &reftitle.examples;
  <para>
   <example>
    <title><function>prev</function> 及相关函数用法示例</title>
    <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
$transport = array('foot', 'bike', 'car', 'plane');
$mode = current($transport); // $mode = 'foot';
$mode = next($transport);    // $mode = 'bike';
$mode = next($transport);    // $mode = 'car';
$mode = prev($transport);    // $mode = 'bike';
$mode = end($transport);     // $mode = 'plane';
?>
]]>
    </programlisting>
   </example>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="notes">
  &reftitle.notes;
  &return.falseproblem;
  <note>
   <simpara>
    你会无法区分包含 <type>boolean</type> &false; 单元的数组开头。要正确遍历可能含有空单元或者单元值为 0 的数组，参见
       <function>each</function> 函数。
   </simpara>
  </note>
 </refsect1>
 <refsect1 role="seealso">
  &reftitle.seealso;
  <para>
   <simplelist>
    <member><function>current</function></member>
    <member><function>end</function></member>
    <member><function>next</function></member>
    <member><function>reset</function></member>
    <member><function>each</function></member>
   </simplelist>
  </para>
 </refsect1>
  </refentry>

